Metro Watch

_"One of the original styles from our debut watch collection and a classic that makes every outfit tick."_ -Deborah Lloyd, Creative Director of kate spade new york

* Round yellow gold tone base metal case with navy blue dial 
* Navy blue strap with buckle closure 
* Water resistance tested at 30M 
* Case measures 30mm (1.81 inches) wide 
* Strap measures 13mm (0.51 inches) wide 